AD_AUXILIARINPUT.NAME: BPReadOnly
AD_AUXILIARINPUT.CODE: @SQL=SELECT 'Y' FROM DUAL WHERE (select count(OBWSHIP_Shipping_Details_id) from OBWSHIP_Shipping left join OBWSHIP_Shipping_Details on OBWSHIP_Shipping_Details.OBWSHIP_Shipping_id = OBWSHIP_Shipping.OBWSHIP_Shipping_id where OBWSHIP_Shipping.OBWSHIP_Shipping_id=@OBWSHIP_Shipping_id@) <> 0

AD_AUXILIARINPUT.NAME: IsSriLankaRecord
AD_AUXILIARINPUT.CODE: @SQL=SELECT 'Y' FROM DUAL WHERE (select count(OBWSHIP_Shipping_Details_id) from OBWSHIP_Shipping left join OBWSHIP_Shipping_Details on OBWSHIP_Shipping_Details.OBWSHIP_Shipping_id = OBWSHIP_Shipping.OBWSHIP_Shipping_id left join c_bpartner on c_bpartner.c_bpartner_id=OBWSHIP_Shipping.c_bpartner_id left join c_bpartner_location on c_bpartner_location.c_bpartner_id=c_bpartner.c_bpartner_id left join c_location on c_location.c_location_id=c_bpartner_location.c_location_id left join c_country on c_country.c_country_id=c_location.c_country_id where OBWSHIP_Shipping.OBWSHIP_Shipping_id=@OBWSHIP_Shipping_id@ and c_country.name ='Sri Lanka') <> 0
